<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invite cannot be used</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .alert {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{AppName}}</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello, {{FriendName}}!</h2>
        
        <p>Unfortunately, the invite sent by <strong>{{InviterName}}</strong> cannot be used.</p>
        
        <div class="alert">
            <strong>Reason:</strong> You already have an account on our platform.
        </div>
        
        <p>Friend invites are only valid for <strong>new users</strong> who don't have an account yet.</p>
        
        <p>Since you are already a registered user, you can:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Continue using your account normally</li>
            <li>Send invites to your friends who don't have an account yet</li>
            <li>Share our platform through other means</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Thank you for being part of the {{AppName}} community!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 {{AppName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 